ludes steps of: connecting to a mobile device via a network; receiving a scan execution request from the mobile device; scanning a document and generating corresponding scan image data according to the scan execution request; and automatically transmitting the scan image data to a destination according to the scan execution request after completing scanning the document. A computer program for controlling the scanning apparatus is also provided.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>